Package com.embeddedunveiled.serial.ftp

Encapsulates behavior and environment centered around serial port communication involving file transfers using x/y/z modem protocols etc.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ISerialComXmodemProgress
    The interface ISerialComXmodemProgress should be implemented by class who wish to know how many blocks have been sent or received using Xmodem protocol.
    ISerialComYmodemProgress
    The interface ISerialComYmodemProgress should be implemented by class who wish to know how many blocks have been sent or received using Ymodem protocol.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    SerialComFTPCMDAbort
    Acts as a messenger between application and this library to specify whether sending/receiving file should continue or be aborted.
    SerialComXModem
    Implements state machine based file transfer based on XMODEM-128 file transfer protocol.
    SerialComXModem1K
    Implements state machine based file transfer based on XMODEM-1K file transfer protocol.
    SerialComXModemCRC
    Implements state machine based file transfer based on XMODEM-CRC file transfer protocol.
    SerialComYModem1K
    Implements state machine based file transfer based on YMODEM-1K file transfer protocol.
    SerialComYModemCRC
    Implements state machine based file transfer based on YMODEM-CRC file transfer protocol.

Package com.embeddedunveiled.serial.ftp Description

Encapsulates behavior and environment centered around serial port communication involving file transfers using x/y/z modem protocols etc.
